none.description:
{Sorrow}

Decreases Morale of target enemy unit by -1.

While Sorrow lasts, Morale bonuses cannot raise that unit above -1 Morale.

basic.description:
{Basic Sorrow}

Decreases Morale of target enemy unit by -1.

While Sorrow lasts, Morale bonuses cannot raise that unit above -1 Morale.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Sorrow}

Decreases Morale of target enemy unit by -2.

While Sorrow lasts, Morale bonuses cannot raise that unit above -2 Morale.

expert.description:
{Expert Sorrow}

Decreases Morale of all enemy units by -2.

While Sorrow lasts, Morale bonuses cannot raise affected units above -2 Morale.
